title: StartMonologue
---
Roxi: Welcome! I'm Roxi! I know, first days can be overwhelming, but don't worry — I'll guide you through everything :)
Roxi: This room is your main hub - a calm place to plan, build, and prepare between working days
Roxi: But before anything else . . .  let's take a look at your cafe space
Roxi: Walk to the highlighted <color=\#7013c2>Cafe Builder</color> and press <color=\#7013c2>E</color> to interact
===

title: BuilderMonologue
---
Roxi: This is your <color=\#7013c2>Blueprint Builder</color>. Here you can remove, place, and rotate everything in your cafe
Roxi: Hmm . . .  it looks a bit rough right now. Let's clean things up first
Roxi: Press <color=\#7013c2>X</color> to enter <color=\#7013c2>Remove Mode</color>. While in this mode, <color=\#7013c2>Left Click</color> objects to remove and put them into your Inventory
===

title: PlaceMonologue
---
Roxi: Much better already!! Now it's time to place furniture back and shape your cafe
Roxi: Press <color=\#7013c2>X</color> again to exit <color=\#7013c2>Remove Mode</color>. Open the <color=\#7013c2>All</color> tab to see everything you own
Roxi: Select an Furniture, then <color=\#7013c2>Left Click</color> to place it in the cafe! Make it cozy!!
===

title: BuyMonologue
---
Roxi: A cafe needs supplies!
Roxi: To brew coffee or unlock new furniture, you'll need to visit the <color=\#7013c2>Shop</color>.
Roxi: Here you can buy ingredients, decorations and machines for your cafe
Roxi: Buy <color=\#cc170a>10 Coffee Beans</color> to prepare for your first day
===

title: DoorMonologue
---
Roxi: Everything's set — time to open!
Roxi: Walk to the <color=\#7013c2>highlighted door</color> and press <color=\#7013c2>E</color> to <color=\#7013c2>enter your cafe</color>
Roxi: This will start your first day as a cafe owner
===

title: CafeIntroMonologue
---
Roxi: Welcome to your cafe! This is where the magic happens :)
Roxi: You'll serve customers, make drinks and grow your cozy little business
Roxi: Let's wait for our first customer!
===

title: NPCMonologue
---
Roxi: Here comes your first customer!
Roxi: Customers will only arrive if there's a seat available, so make sure your cafe has enough chairs
Roxi: Press <color=\#7013c2>E</color> to <color=\#7013c2>interact</color> and take their order
Roxi: Prepare their drink at the <color=\#7013c2>coffee machine</color>. Be quick — their <color=\#cc170a>patience bar</color> appears above their head
Roxi: With some of them, you can also <color=\#7013c2>chat</color> to build friendship!!
===

title: RecipeBookMonologue
---
Roxi: Not sure how to make a drink?
Roxi: Press <color=\#7013c2>TAB</color> to open your <color=\#7013c2>Recipe Book</color>. Here you can see all unlocked recipes and the ingredients needed for each one
Roxi: On the left side, you'll find active customer orders. Click an order to view its recipe instantly
===
title: MakeCoffeeMonologue
---
Roxi: Let's brew your first coffee
Roxi: Get a <color=\#cc170a>Mug</color> and <color=\#cc170a>Ingredients</color> from the highlighted <color=\#7013c2>Storage Drawers</color>. Press <color=\#7013c2>E</color> to open and select your Item. Then walk to the <color=\#7013c2>coffee machine</color>
Roxi: While holding an item, press <color=\#7013c2>E</color> to <color=\#7013c2>add</color> it to a machine
Roxi: And there you go — your first coffee!
Roxi: (Later on, recipes will become more complex and exciting. There is a lot to unlock!)
===
title: EndMonologue
---
Roxi: Each cafe day ends after some time  .. There's a day and night cycle, and customers depend on the time of day
Roxi: Once all guests leave, you'll get a daily recap of your progress. After that, the door back to the <color=\#7013c2>hub</color> unlocks
Roxi: .. And don't forget — <color=\#cc170a>every Sunday</color>, rent is due! ..
Roxi: That's all you need to know. Enjoy your first day and have fun!
===
